IR:

* Iron Raptor nodded.*

" Tell me about it, and we're going to have one Pit of a time manufacturing 
the materials to rebuild it."

* She continued to walk towards the Ark even as Prowl hopped off and began 
to walk beside her, looking around as she did.
But she simply nodded to Prowls question.*

" I'm posative she is, I'm picking up her program signature on my scanners. 
She still active too."

* And with that she walked up to the vert beginning of the wreckage, 
eventually finding herself walking on top of it and continuing to find the 
location to start digging.*


Desmonus:

* Desmonus simply kept walking at the two males came up and walked beside 
her, uncrossing her arms and simply keeping pace.
She noticed Bloodystrike moving closer to her, about ready to answer him 
when she heard Repltilica speak up.
A wicked smile turning her lips as he moved closer to her and suggested 
something.*

"Hmm...I HAVE been on my feet all day and they are feeling a bit tired...and 
cold."

* She took hold of Bloodystrikes arm and leaned against Reptilica, simply 
getting close to smell how well his mech-fluid would taste when she began to 
feast...*
